verbose_text: Here, we demonstrate that in chronic lymphocytic leukemia (CLL) cells, Tnv-6 causes non genotoxic cytotoxicity, without adversely affecting human clonogenic hematopoietic progenitors in vitro, or murine hematopoiesis.
evidence: Tnv-6 causes non-genotoxic cytotoxicity, without adversely affecting human clonogenic hematopoietic progenitors in vitro, or murine hematopoiesis
